BACK FROM WESTERN CABLE SHOW AND CHRISTMAS


12/28/99
  Work on P1 directory.
  - added mpeg2.c to demux

12/29/99
  Testing the P1 directory.
  Without RC, bypassing and splicing works.
  Video breakup with RC!

  The problem seems to be in the change of frstSlcPos to frstSlcPtr in PicStat.
  It now points to the next byte after the first slice start code, instead of
  the first byte of the first slice start code.  As a result, we need to modify
  videoes.c to supress the generation of the first slice start code!
